    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-400d8a354e-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "WELCOME TO OUR NEW MEMBERS!! The months of August/September saw a great increase in the COC's membership roster, due primarily to:",
      "text_length": 130
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-2572bd3252-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "A. Karl Nolte's excellent series of Orienteering seminars at REI followed by a Beginners' Training Event at Woodland Park.",
      "text_length": 122
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-c43f3221a0-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "B. The COC's 7-week Orienteering Display at the Pacific Science Center in conjunction with the Center's Map Exhibit put together by the National Archives.",
      "text_length": 154
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-08aab7b865-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "We invite all new members and those new to Orienteering to our October 13 (note date change) Beginners' meet at Seward Park in Seattle. See you there!",
      "text_length": 150
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-a58da8befd-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "In a more serious vein, many of you are already aware that Corrie and I will be leaving the Seattle area for Cedar Rapids, Iowa on 1 November. We've enjoyed our association with the club and hope to see you all at the October meeting and meet. -Mike",
      "text_length": 250
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-heading-6319fc2756-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "EVENTS",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-329cdb8c1a-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "On September 8, Karl Nolte presented a Beginners' Training Event at Woodland Park in Seattle. This event was a 'hands on' finale to Karl's two map-and-compass seminars at REI during August. Karl procured and field-checked a new map of Woodland Park and then used it to put together a 9-point course. Karl's lecture and training series were very positively received and have resulted in a new group of Orienteers in our midst. Thanks to Karl for his efforts.",
      "text_length": 457
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-0db19d734c-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "BEGINNERS TRAINING EVENT - Woodland Park",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-e663be2c8d-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Mike Schuh - 27 minutes",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-4c5a954107-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Berith Larsson - 30",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-02efe728dc-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Richard Lacey - 35",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-54db341c48-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "G\u00f6ran and Robert Larsson - 38",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-7ba469bb65-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Joe Dawson - 58 (plus 11 other finishers)",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-e3964c34cb-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "On September 16, Einar Storakers set up a series of challenging courses in Area 33 at Fort Lewis. This area has become one of the clubs' favorite meet sites due to the rolling terrain and many natural features. Due to the publicity efforts of Len Englund and Celeste Neuffer, we had participants from both the Orienteering Association of British Columbia and the University of Idaho Orienteering Club. The weather was 'patches of clouds, but no rain' and we all participated in excellent orienteering and friendship.",
      "text_length": 516
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-57e21c5640-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "RED COURSE",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-1741be6249-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "G\u00f6ran Larsson (COC) - 51:40",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-e5d7faba3d-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Tony Byrne (OABC) - 1:06:30",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-a79bb56bbc-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Ross Burnett (OABC) - 1:11:00",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-41d20d7dd6-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Dave Enger (COC) - 1:16:15",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-2fa935bdf0-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Bruce Manning (UofIdaho) - 1:21:10",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-92f9b4df09-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Allan Rouley (UofIdaho) - 1:22:20",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-9fb8bc6848-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Mike Fiedler (COC) - 1:44:50",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-ecbe4d94be-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Corrie Fiedler (COC) - 2:13:00",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-2ee690f613-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Bill Oliver (UofIdaho) - 2:37:00",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-5aaf8eecc6-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "YELLOW COURSE",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-9e074cab3b-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Berith Larsson (COC) - 34:10",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-984e01c19a-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Eric Englund (COC) - 1:07:20",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-6905e60b17-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Karl and Gibson Nolte (COC) - 1:37:00",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-4ce8886ba0-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Nancy Ward (UofIdaho) - 1:38:30",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-530a6744c7-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "MacDonalds (COC) - 2:01:10",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-c03c45e48c-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "WHITE COURSE",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-469125c82c-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Larry Broughton, Leonard Bahr, and Brett Billings (UofIdaho) - 43:30",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-13b8334255-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Richard Lacy (COC) - 59:10",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-44c3147c31-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Everett and Verlyn",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-heading-c45e7abc57-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "COC SHORTS",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-e949f452f7-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Thanks to Charlie Bock, Gary and Debbie MacDonald, Dave Enger, and Celeste Neuffer for following through on our help-wanted notices last month.",
      "text_length": 143
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-15773c35c4-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Help Wanted (continued from last issue)",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-972390bf88-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "a. Obtain map of the UW Arboretum for canoe orienteering. b. Begin organization of Trim Orienteering course in a city park (we have ideas, possible sponsor) c. Obtain map of Capital Woods State Park in Olympia area for future meets d. Work with Cle Elum Club in mapping a Cle Elum site for future joint meet e. Organize an Orienteering Course through UW Experimental College.",
      "text_length": 379
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-d490ba6804-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "On July 15, the COC held a bon voyage party for Tom and Annette Stewart, in which they were presented with a lifetime membership to the club. We recently received the following note from Tom in Hawaii:",
      "text_length": 201
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-6ab6539ca4-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Dear Members of Cascade Orienteering Club,",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-a672c2c044-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "I would like to thank you very sincerely for honoring me with the lifetime membership in a great organization. My family and I miss the Pacific Northwest very much, but not nearly as much as we miss the great people associated with it. We really appreciated your warm friendship. To all those who really keep the club going, I will extend every courtesy if you should ever visit Hawaii. The Stewart family fully intends on returning to the Seattle area in the future. We hope to see you all again.",
      "text_length": 497
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-9c61fca7d9-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Tom Stewart 3633-C Porter Loop Wahiawa, Hawaii 96786 (808) 62? 6062",
      "text_length": 71
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-heading-7f1f888f42-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "COMING EVENTS",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-heading-958a633700-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "October 8",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-f7eeda5c5b-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "7:00 pm: Short discussion of Orienteering for newcomers",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-1ffa850735-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "7:30 pm: October business meeting at the Greenlake Library",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-68f78813e3-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "The meeting will be followed by a slide show/talk by Rob Corkran. Rob will talk on his recent orienteering experiences in Scandinavia.",
      "text_length": 134
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-heading-a7be562759-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "October 13",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-283bb5499b-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "10 am: Saturday Beginners meet and intermediate score orienteering meet at Seward Park in Seattle",
      "text_length": 97
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-b551a91b02-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Follow the red/white markers up the hill to the registration area. (Remember to bring a watch if you plan on running the score orienteering course)",
      "text_length": 147
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-heading-6a9860a9ce-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "November 17",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-a548289c25-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "10 am: Orienteering meet at St. Edwards State Park in Kirkland",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-98e5ab2e40-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "This will be our club's first meet at this new state park, and our initial scouting shows it to have beautiful orienteering terrain. Follow the red/white markers through the main gate to the registration area. Meet director, Charlie Bock.",
      "text_length": 238
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-heading-75188d425c-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "December 10",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-list_item-9883f636fb-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "7:30 pm: December business meeting at the Greenlake Library",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-93fad39fbb-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "NOTE: DATE CHANGE OF SEWARD PARK MEET - SOME INCORRECT DATE INFO HAS BEEN DISTRIBUTED TO SOME MEMBERS",
      "text_length": 101
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1979-10_11-paragraph-13df7ce24d-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Join us for our October meeting at Greenlake Library and hear slide talk on Orienteering in Scandinavia by Rob Corkran.",
      "text_length": 119
    }
  ]
}
